list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment:
The beginnings of new horizons.
Instructions now auto pool via reflect! YAY! Created a console utility to easily create instruction boilerplates.
Created a couple of instructions to test implementation, and provide proof of concept.
Currently we have fully rendering help strings, pool peeks, pool keys, list all instructions.
Re-created the help instruction with 'console create'
Minor: Added a message for when an invalid number of switch arguments are parsed. Fixed incorrect auto pool statement placement that caused instructions to not pool if they weren't using a specific constructor overload. Fixed where console's show success would re-parse the command to get the result, instead of using the result it already had.
